        <p class="text-amber-700 font-medium">△ Stamp 0 uncertain—ISD may question financial self-sufficiency with €1,500/month given Dublin costs. Would need to demonstrate savings or choose cheaper location. Advised to increase income or consider Portugal/Spain with lower thresholds.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

